      <title>中国经济复苏取决于最富裕城市的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-19/china-s-richest-cities-show-limits-of-1-trillion-debt-swap-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贫困省份的财政困境正蔓延至长期以来被认为不受经济放缓影响的富裕地区。这威胁着整个国家的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-19/china-s-richest-cities-show-limits-of-1-trillion-debt-swap-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当政府停止支出时，实际上哪些设施会被关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/what-actually-happens-when-the-us-government-shuts-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦政府停摆可能会造成混乱，数千名工作人员被迫休假，其中大多数人无法按时领到工资。纳税人将得不到回电，在一年中最繁忙的旅行周之一，机场排队的人可能会更多，许多国家公园也将关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/what-actually-happens-when-the-us-government-shuts-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 21:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班呼吁欧盟：等待特朗普决定是否延长对俄制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/orban-risks-russia-sanctions-lapse-with-demand-on-trump-timeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班告诉欧盟领导人，他希望等到他的盟友唐纳德·特朗普就职后再决定是否延长欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/orban-risks-russia-sanctions-lapse-with-demand-on-trump-timeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持众议院共和党政府融资计划，推迟债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/house-republicans-say-they-have-deal-on-funding-us-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普与众议院共和党人达成协议，避免美国政府关门，并暂停联邦债务上限两年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/house-republicans-say-they-have-deal-on-funding-us-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默任命贸易资深人士曼德尔森为英国驻美国大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命资深工党人物和贸易专家彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 为英国驻美国大使，以避免英国受到唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 征收关税的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
